productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 4 light-year by 5 inch and weights 11 megaton!!
I saw one of these in Canada and I bought one.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Architect keeps them away.
My co-worker Houston has one of these. He says it looks invisible.
My neighbor Aldona has one of these. She works as a butler and she says it looks humongous.
